{"tid":644887,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足睇《隊長小翼》大？","createTime":"2018-04-27T14:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T02:36:07.000Z","uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fba3f3e5c482145ebe274310081f890eac976d34","tid":644887,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"日本旅遊資訊網站「粹日本」（IKIDANE NIPPON）上周日在其Facebook專頁，刊出一篇關於日本東京都葛飾區之旅遊資訊時，將港人耳熟能詳的日本著名動畫《足球小將》寫為中國之譯名《隊長小翼》，結果遭到網民質疑，指「中港澳譯名係足球小將，而且係現在進行式。台灣譯名係足球小將-翼。幾時出現隊長小翼呢？」 <br />\n<br />\n「粹日本」專頁負責人今早回覆該名網民時指，「作品譯名按出版社集英社要求，現時香港譯名定為「隊長小翼」；謝謝。」 <br />\n<br />\n《足球小將》作者為高橋陽一，於1981年開始連載，原作之日文名稱為《キャプテン翼》，英譯為《Captain Tsubasa》，香港一方獲得版權後，將名字改為《足球小將》，結果大受歡迎，成為幾代香港人的集體回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/04-27-2018/45473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F04-27-2018%2F45473&d=0dcvmh6q41fXOr6Ir49lSxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=b1f4f490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/04-27-2018/45473</a>"},{"pid":"a70847f6cd8fcf1fa223c5249bf7eb8aee2d0f4a","tid":644887,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"樓豬70後"},{"pid":"80ac87fa05e28877d222c2c596b35bbd50746915","tid":644887,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a70847f6cd8fcf1fa223c5249bf7eb8aee2d0f4a","tid":644887,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"樓豬70後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"00後"},{"pid":"135385fa9a2bba37fa41f79ec02962b28ab78445","tid":644887,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"個小字係邊到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80a6fc239abd759aded77376006caba94212cb0","tid":644887,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T17:25:04.000Z","msg":"廿頭身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal